00:28:13,170 --> 00:28:14,400
Ang dalawang putahe.

493
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:16,060
Paa ng manok at mabahong tokwa.

494
00:28:22,570 --> 00:28:24,770
Dati kang kumakapit sa akin

495
00:28:24,800 --> 00:28:25,940
buong araw,

496
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,450
pero ngayon...

497
00:28:28,490 --> 00:28:30,550
Hindi ko alam kung paano ko ito ipapaliwanag kahit papaano.

498
00:28:34,480 --> 00:28:35,550
Tumigil ka na sa paglalaro.

499
00:28:36,490 --> 00:28:37,240
Bumalik ka.

500
00:28:37,580 --> 00:28:39,030
Malapit na akong matapos sa level na ito.

501
00:28:39,030 --> 00:28:40,430
Kahit ano.

502
00:28:41,530 --> 00:28:42,630
Sige.

503
00:28:42,970 --> 00:28:45,300
Saka huwag mo akong ite-text mamaya
para lang sigawan ako.

504
00:28:47,720 --> 00:28:48,290
Paalam.

505
00:28:50,080 --> 00:28:51,740
Ayaw mo ba talagang mag-stay?

506
00:28:53,210 --> 00:28:54,810
Gusto mo ba talaga akong mag-stay?

507
00:28:56,070 --> 00:28:56,990
Mawala.

508
00:28:59,100 --> 00:29:00,000
Paalam.

509
00:29:25,200 --> 00:29:27,000
Naku. Umalis na talaga siya.

510
00:30:33,900 --> 00:30:35,100
Ang mga iyon ba ay

511
00:30:35,950 --> 00:30:37,310
mga alaala ng déjà vu

512
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:39,550
kailanman

513
00:30:40,750 --> 00:30:42,450
bumalik?

514
00:30:44,190 --> 00:30:45,490
O...

515
00:30:46,550 --> 00:30:49,350
Nabura na ba talaga ako
sa alaala ng lahat?

516
00:30:53,080 --> 00:31:00,430
[Epilogo]

517
00:31:04,630 --> 00:31:08,580
[Para sa iyo]

518
00:31:38,470 --> 00:31:39,310
Hong?

519
00:31:40,510 --> 00:31:41,570
Ano ang ginagawa mo?

520
00:31:43,060 --> 00:31:44,120
Ako ay

521
00:31:45,430 --> 00:31:46,690
nanonood ng mga bulalakaw.

522
00:31:46,690 --> 00:31:48,150
Nanonood ng mga bulalakaw?

523
00:31:48,960 --> 00:31:51,220
Pero maghapon na ngayon.

524
00:31:51,630 --> 00:31:53,230
Alam kong may mga bulalakaw
sa araw.

525
00:31:53,230 --> 00:31:54,070
Pero...

526
00:31:54,290 --> 00:31:55,750
Sa tingin ko hindi natin ito makikita.

527
00:31:56,890 --> 00:31:57,880
Tanga.

528
00:31:58,080 --> 00:32:00,260
Iyon ay dahil hindi ka tumingin nang mabuti.

529
00:32:00,260 --> 00:32:01,840
Tingnan mong mabuti.

530
00:32:01,860 --> 00:32:03,130
Tingnan mong mabuti?

531
00:32:04,630 --> 00:32:05,800
Ano ang ibig mong sabihin?

532
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:08,540
Gusto mo bang mag-wish sa
mga shooting star?

533
00:32:09,110 --> 00:32:10,210
Pakiusap.

534
00:32:10,380 --> 00:32:12,820
Narinig ko na ang kwentong iyan simula pa noong bata pa ako.

535
00:32:13,300 --> 00:32:15,500
May mga pangarap na ba talaga na natupad?

536
00:32:16,550 --> 00:32:18,510
Mali ang ginagawa niyong lahat.

537
00:32:18,780 --> 00:32:19,920
Maling paraan?

538
00:32:20,420 --> 00:32:21,180
Ano?

539
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:22,750
Makinig nang mabuti.

540
00:32:22,750 --> 00:32:23,720
Minsan ko lang sasabihin.

541
00:32:23,720 --> 00:32:24,820
Sige.

542
00:32:26,710 --> 00:32:28,850
Ito ay isang piraso ng bulalakaw.

543
00:32:28,960 --> 00:32:30,420
Isang piraso ng bulalakaw.

544
00:32:30,510 --> 00:32:31,980
Kailangan mo

545
00:32:32,010 --> 00:32:34,610
itapon mo itong piraso ng bulalakaw
sa dagat

546
00:32:34,900 --> 00:32:36,100
kapag dumating ito.

547
00:32:38,670 --> 00:32:40,600
Kapag ang enerhiya at ang iyong nais

548
00:32:40,600 --> 00:32:41,940
pagsamahin,

549
00:32:42,670 --> 00:32:44,070
matutupad ang iyong hiling.

550
00:32:44,540 --> 00:32:46,210
Talaga?

551
00:32:47,780 --> 00:32:49,010
Gusto mo bang subukan?

552
00:32:49,010 --> 00:32:50,680
Sa susunod na lang.

553
00:32:50,980 --> 00:32:53,440
Kailangan ko nang bumalik para tumulong
sa guesthouse.

554
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,740
Tumataas ang tubig.

555
00:32:55,050 --> 00:32:56,650
Gusto mo bang sumama sa akin pabalik?

556
00:32:57,350 --> 00:32:58,120
Iwan mo na ako.

557
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:59,120
Bumalik ka na ngayon.

558
00:32:59,120 --> 00:32:59,960
Pumunta.

559
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:00,560
Sige.

560
00:33:00,560 --> 00:33:01,320
Mag-ingat ka.

561
00:33:01,320 --> 00:33:02,360
Sige, naiintindihan ko.

562
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:02,850
Paalam.

563
00:33:02,850 --> 00:33:03,750
Sige, paalam.

564
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,380
Magche-check in ka na ba?

565
00:33:53,530 --> 00:33:59,810
[Susunod na Episode]

566
00:33:54,440 --> 00:33:55,610
Chen Haowei.

567
00:33:55,610 --> 00:33:56,410
Ginoo.

568
00:33:56,410 --> 00:33:57,610
Nagche-check in ka ba?

569
00:33:58,350 --> 00:34:00,020
Gusto kita!

570
00:34:00,020 --> 00:34:01,690
Gusto kita!

571
00:34:03,930 --> 00:34:05,760
Narinig mo na ba ang tungkol sa memorya ng selula?

572
00:34:05,780 --> 00:34:07,230
o memorya ng katawan?

573
00:34:07,250 --> 00:34:08,480
Maaaring makalimutan ng iyong isipan,

574
00:34:08,989 --> 00:34:10,760
pero ang puso mo ay hindi kailanman magiging ganoon.

575
00:34:10,940 --> 00:34:12,199
Natatandaan mo na ba ngayon?
